node-exporter-mycloud
======================

This project packages the Prometheus node_exporter as an installable app for
Western Digital My Cloud (OS5) NAS devices. It bundles and builds on third-party
components:

1. mksapkg-OS5
   - Source: https://github.com/WDCommunity/wdpksrc
   - License: BSD 3-Clause (Copyright (c) 2018, WDCommunity)
   - The packaging tool that produces the WD `.bin` (APKG) format. Vendored as
     a prebuilt Linux x86-64 binary and executed only inside the build Docker
     image. Not modified.

2. Package structure / scripts
   - Modeled on the ZeroTier package from WDCommunity/wdpksrc (BSD 3-Clause),
     which targets the My Cloud EX2 Ultra on OS5, and on the sibling project
     tailscale-mycloud (BSD 3-Clause).

3. Prometheus node_exporter
   - Source: https://github.com/prometheus/node_exporter  (https://prometheus.io)
   - License: Apache License 2.0 (Copyright The Prometheus Authors)
   - NOT vendored in this repository. The official static `linux-armv7` build is
     downloaded from the project's GitHub Releases at build time and verified
     against its published `sha256sums.txt` checksum before being placed in the
     package.

